Welcome to Plasma Donation

Save lives by donating plasma

Donate Now

Why Donate Plasma?

  • Plasma helps patients with immune deficiencies
  • Plasma is used in the treatment of various diseases
  • Your donation can make a difference in someone's life

Donation Process

  1. Check eligibility requirements
  2. Schedule an appointment
  3. Arrive at the donation center
  4. Undergo screening and donation
  5. Receive a thank you and refreshments
